  <description>PDK WiMAC wireless communication daughtercard, shown in its mounted orientation. Its footprint and header locations are calibrated from the manufacturer Red 4 installation graphic. Twenty physical header contacts are mapped; their electrical assignments remain generic pending a verified factory pinout.</description>
